# Changelog

## [1.1.0] - 2025-11-01

### Added
- Advanced audio analysis modules (chord, structure, rhythm, timbre, melody, dynamics)
- Selective analysis options for faster targeted analysis
- Quiet option for CLI with test coverage
- Progress bar accuracy and user experience improvements

### Changed
- Improved accuracy of audio analysis modules
- Enhanced key/chord detection with drop chorus logic
- Major codebase improvements with enhanced tooling and testing
- Updated package dependencies

### Fixed
- CI test failures resolved
- BPM selection bug
- Progress bar update issues
- Audio analysis accuracy and stability improvements
- Noise audio confidence threshold in key detector test
- Coverage configuration to report correct metrics (85%)
- Unused global lint errors

### Documentation
- Fixed typos in README files
- Updated progress flag usage documentation
- Clarified commit and branch rules

### Development
- Configured black formatter and fixed lint issues
- Applied black and isort formatting

## [1.0.0] - 2025-05-29

### Added
- Initial release
- BPM (tempo) detection from audio files
- Musical key detection
- Command-line interface for audio analysis
